---
layout: base
---

<div class="py-8">
  <h2 class="text-3xl">Talks</h2>

  <p class="prose">
      Here is a collection of talks and videos I have given at various meetups and conferences.
  </p>

  <ul class="list-none space-y-6">
      {% for title, talk in talks %}
      <li class="flex gap-x-4 items-center">
        {% set description = "Remote Talk" if talk.remote else "In-Person Talk" %}
        <div class="" title="{{description}}">
        <span class="sr-only">{{description}}</span>
          {% icon 'computer-desktop' if talk.remote else 'user' %}
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-baseline">
          <a class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900" href="{{ talk.url }}">{{ title }}</a>
          <div class="flex gap-x-2 items-baseline">
            <span class="text-gray-700 text-sm">{{ talk.location }}</span>
            <span class="text-gray-500 text-xs flex-shrink-0 mr-2">{{ talk.date }}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</div>
